info.headline: Wind Advisory issued January 14 at 11:48AM PST until January 14 at 2:00PM PST by NWS Monterey
info.description: ...WIND ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 2 PM PST THIS AFTERNOON... * WHAT...South winds 20 to 30 mph with gusts up to 50 mph expected. * WHERE...Monterey and San Benito counties. * WHEN...Until 2 PM PST Saturday. * IMPACTS...Gusty winds could blow around unsecured objects. Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may result.
info.instruction: Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.
